# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Supply-Link — Root Workspace Environment Variables
# These are optional values for local release and deployment tasks.
# Copy to .env and fill in values. NEVER commit .env to version control.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# GitHub personal access token for any manual GitHub release or package task.
# Generate at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# GITHUB_TOKEN=

# Stellar secret key for testnet contract deployment.
# Fund the account with Friendbot before use: https://friendbot.stellar.org
# STELLAR_SECRET_KEY=

# Vercel deployment token for manual frontend deployments.
# Generate at: https://vercel.com/account/tokens
# VERCEL_TOKEN=
